WEBVTT

00:10.376 --> 00:13.270
I remember
when I was a little girl,

00:13.273 --> 00:16.267
My dada took me to the circus --

00:16.270 --> 00:19.534
The greatest show on earth.

00:19.534 --> 00:24.564
There were clowns and elephants
and dancing bears...

00:24.563 --> 00:27.657
And a beautiful lady
in pink tights

00:27.660 --> 00:30.984
Flew high above our heads.

00:30.991 --> 00:33.726
And as I sat there watching,

00:33.722 --> 00:37.345
I had the feeling
that something was missing.

00:37.352 --> 00:39.208
I don't know what,

00:39.216 --> 00:42.151
But when it was all over,

00:42.147 --> 00:45.640
I said to myself,

00:45.644 --> 00:49.646
"is that all there is
to the circus?"

00:49.640 --> 00:53.104
Uh-oh.
Here comes trouble.

00:54.435 --> 00:58.028
¶ I know what you must be saying
to yourselves ¶

00:58.032 --> 01:01.555
¶ "if that's the way
she feels about it ¶

01:01.562 --> 01:04.596
¶ why doesn't
she just end it all?" ¶

01:04.593 --> 01:06.189
¶ oh, no ¶

01:06.191 --> 01:08.417
Cat's got his tongue.

01:08.423 --> 01:14.182
I'm not ready yet
for that final disappointment.

01:14.184 --> 01:18.506
For I know just as well as I'm
standing here talking to you,

01:18.514 --> 01:21.368
When that final moment comes

01:21.377 --> 01:24.232
And I'm breathing
my last breath...

01:26.272 --> 01:29.536
...I'll be saying to myself,
"is that all?

01:29.537 --> 01:32.461
Is that all there is to dying?"

